properties.areaDesc: South Central Elko County; Ruby Mountains and East Humboldt Range; Northern Elko County; Southeastern Elko County
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 6 at 9:00PM PST until February 7 at 8:00AM PST by NWS Elko NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to 55 mph.

* WHERE...Northern Elko County, Southeastern Elko County, Ruby
Mountains/East Humboldt Range and South Central Elko County.
Strongest winds are expected over mountains, higher elevation
stretches of roads, such as Pequop Summit on I80, and along
eastern slopes of mountains, such as the Ruby Valley and Clover
Valley areas.

* WHEN...Until 8 AM PST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM PST FRIDAY
